import React from 'react';
import { BrowserRouter, Redirect, Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom';
import './App.css';

import NavBar from './shared/NavBar'
import ItemsPage from './items/ItemsPage'
import ItemForm from './items/ItemForm'
import ItemPage from './items/ItemPage'
import ContainersPage from './containers/ContainersPage'
import ContainerForm from './containers/ContainerForm'
import ContainerPage from './containers/ContainerPage'
import SampleTypeCategoriesPage from './containerTypeCategories/SampleTypeCategoriesPage'
import SampleTypeCategoryForm from './containerTypeCategories/SampleTypeCategoryForm'
import SampleTypeCategoryPage from './containerTypeCategories/SampleTypeCategoryPage'

export default function App() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <NavBar />
      <Switch>
        <Route exact path="/items" render={(props) => <ItemsPage {...props} />} />
        <Route exact path="/items/new" render={(props) => <ItemForm {...props} />} />
        <Route exact path="/items/:id" render={(props) => <ItemPage {...props} />} />

        <Route exact path="/containers" render={(props) => <ContainersPage {...props} />} />
        <Route exact path="/containers/new" render={(props) => <ContainerForm {...props} />} />
        <Route exact path="/containers/:id" render={(props) => <ContainerPage {...props} />} />

        <Route exact path="/container_type_categories" render={(props) => <SampleTypeCategoriesPage {...props} />} />
        <Route exact path="/container_type_categories/new" render={(props) => <SampleTypeCategoryForm {...props} />} />
        <Route exact path="/container_type_categories/:id" render={(props) => <SampleTypeCategoryPage {...props} />} />
      </Switch>
    </BrowserRouter>
  );
}
